title: APNewsBreak: George Harrison, Gaye up for Songwriters Hall
text: > Entertainment APNewsBreak: George Harrison, Gaye up for Songwriters Hall FILE - In this Feb. 8, 2015 file photo, Madonna performs at the 57th annual Grammy Awards in Los Angeles. Madonna, along with George Harrison, Marvin Gaye, Jimi Hendrix, John Mellencamp and Tom Petty are among the A-list contenders nominated for the 2016 Songwriters Hall of Fame. The 2016 Songwriters Hall of Fame Annual Induction and Awards Gala will take place June 9, 2016. (Photo by John Shearer/Invision/AP)
